  "description": [
    "Friday December 22 1961 Memorial Meet Here Will Honor Martyr The memory of a Polish leader who committed suicide in protest to Hitlers extermination of the Jews will be hon ored at a special public meeting Jan 3 at 8 pm in the audi torium of Cong Anshei Israel Workmens Circle and the Jewish Labor Committee will join in the sponsorship of the memorial meeting for Arthur Zigelboim leader of the Jew ish Labor Bund and member of the Polish government in exile Mr Zigelboim seeking to bring world awareness to the plight of European Jews committed suicide in London in 1943 The memorial meeting is open to the public without charge and there will be no solicitation Coming to Tucson as guest speaker for the meeting will be Nathan Gierovitz execu tive secretary for the Califor nia district of the Jewish La bor Committee Mr Giero vitz will come here from Los Angeles BIRTHS To Dr and Mrs Richard Federhar a daughter Lisa Joy 7 lbs 4 oz on Dec 11 Grandparents are Mr and Mrs Alex Federhar and Mrs Anna Winter all of Tucson To Mr and Mrs Jerome Rosenberg a daughter Lisa Ann 7 lbs oz on"
  ],
